Metadata-Version: 1.0
Name: zipeggs
Version: 1.0.1
Summary: Zip flattened out eggs back again
Home-page: https://github.com/tamizhgeek/zipeggs
Author: Azhagu Selvan
Author-email: UNKNOWN
License: Apache 2.0
Description: Buildout when collecting eggs, always flattens out the eggs as directories. We had a requirement where the eggs are needed as zips not as dirs. So this recipe. This will take a folder as input, iterate through the folders in it and create zip archives out of all folders inside it.
Platform: UNKNOWN
